               <p>
                  <hi rend="smallCaps">
                     <persName id="t18500107-name-397" type="witnessName">
                        <interp inst="t18500107-name-397" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                        <interp inst="t18500107-name-397" type="surname" value="GOSTLING"></interp>
                        <interp inst="t18500107-name-397" type="given" value="JAMES"></interp>JAMES GOSTLING</persName>
                  </hi>. I am a carpenter, of Stoke Newington. I was at work at a building in Bloomfield-street, on the 21st Dec.—I left between twelve and one o'clock, to fetch some beer for dinner—when I got back I missed my saw and my dinner, which I had laid out—I found my saw in pawn at the first pawnbroker's I came to.</p>
